And I search for a patient with the NHS number in the find a patient screen
And I open the patient record by clicking on patient FLORINDA DUNNER
When I click choose vaccine button and choose the Flu, SDYY2-24A with 5/5/2025 and click continue
And I assess the patient's yes with the details and date as today and click continue to record consent screen button
And I record yes with the details and click continue to vaccinate button
And I record yes details and date as today and click Continue to Check and confirm screen
Then I need to be able to see the patient FLORINDA DUNNER, 27/3/1957, 32 HOLLAND ROAD, MANCHESTER, M8 4NP and vaccination details on the check and confirm screen
